{"tid":907148,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"大媽港珠澳大橋口岸跳廣場舞　網民：好過在市區跳","createTime":"2018-11-18T14:49:12.000Z","updateTime":"2018-11-18T16:45:15.000Z","uid":20058,"like":19,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"bbd8d8eed6ee19160e31911a6692774fc64c82bc","tid":907148,"uid":20058,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-18T14:49:12.000Z","msg":"自港珠澳大橋上月底通車，人工島旅檢大樓外滿佈旅客。有網民發現，香港口岸外除了有候車或等候出入境的旅客，還有遊客在口岸區跳廣場舞。<br />\n<br />\n網民在facebook「香港突發事故報料區」上載影片發文，指今早近9時，有一群遊客在港珠澳大橋香港口岸跳廣場舞。影片所見，一群遊客聚集在香港口岸旅檢大樓外，跟隨音樂跳起雙人舞，現場背景正播放電視劇集插曲「安守本份」。<br />\n<br />\n有網民不禁慨嘆「邊度有廣場邊度都有大媽舞」，也有網民表示，寧願「大媽」聚集口岸區跳舞，因該處遠離民居，對市民影響較少，「喺度跳咪幾好，又唔阻到居民」、「跳遠啲&hellip;&hellip;盡量遠離市區」。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.mingpao.com/ins/instantnews/web_tc/article/20181118/s00001/1542514134829?fbclid=IwAR0YIVz5xQhmkL-PqWlymLruNc47FbK__d3Hqkh0BbV-1_Cen6UgiI4hGA8\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.mingpao.com%2Fins%2Finstantnews%2Fweb_tc%2Farticle%2F20181118%2Fs00001%2F1542514134829%3Ffbclid%3DIwAR0YIVz5xQhmkL-PqWlymLruNc47FbK__d3Hqkh0BbV-1_Cen6UgiI4hGA8&d=GQ0VIr%2FKcmFeNPLG%2BWrr%2F9ZqoKrPvqrE%2FsQ53lv%2BkYo%3D&h=f4b3d9ec\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.mingpao.com%2Fins%2Finstantnews%2Fweb_tc%2Farticle%2F20181118%2Fs00001%2F1542514134829%3Ffbclid%3DIwAR0YIVz5xQhmkL-PqWlymLruNc47FbK__d3Hqkh0BbV-1_Cen6UgiI4hGA8&h=33f5d95a\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://news.mingpao.com/ins/instantnews/web_tc/article/20181118/s00001/1542514134829?fbclid=IwAR0YIVz5xQhmkL-PqWlymLruNc47FbK__d3Hqkh0BbV-1_Cen6UgiI4hGA8</a><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"69c38b0462850c12197f5381c662cff3374f3441","tid":907148,"uid":20058,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-18T16:00:24.000Z